LineComment.Text: Definizione Parola di Stato: Bit 00: Drive PI: Ready TO Switch "ON" Bit 01: Drive PI: Ready TO Operate Bit 02: Drive PI: Operation Enabled. The Drive Follows the Setpoint Bit 03: Drive PI: Fault Bit 04: Drive PI: Coast Stop (OFF2) command is NOT Active Bit 05: Drive PI: Quick Stop (OFF3) command is NOT Active Bit 06: Drive PI: Switching on inhibited Bit 07: Drive PI: Warning Bit 08: Drive PI: Setpoint/Actual Value deviation within tolerance range. Bit 09: Drive PI: Master control requested Bit 10: Drive PI: Maximum frequency reached OR exceeded Bit 11: Drive PI: Motor at Current/Torque limit Bit 12: Drive PI: Motor Holding Brake Open Bit 13: Drive PI: Motor Overload Bit 14: Drive PI: Motor Rotation (1 = CW; 0 = CCW). Bit 15: Drive PI: Inverter Overload
